{"tid":1604690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"出發前發定個未來 Email, 以防被自殺","createTime":"2019-09-30T04:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T04:58:54.000Z","uid":328322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d291e8cd9ab171983b8924334a3ae30e1dc4e9b3","tid":1604690,"uid":328322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"即使有其他人在場, 甚至記者, 都未必報到自己既名<br />\n其實有個 App 要 Boomerang 既 Email Client, 可以做到 delay send<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.boomerang.boomerangapp&amp;hl=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.boomerang.boomerangapp%26hl%3Dzh_HK&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1SLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=5bdbcba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.boomerang.boomerangapp&amp;hl=zh_HK</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/email-client-boomerang-mail/id1236906322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Femail-client-boomerang-mail%2Fid1236906322&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1SLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=112d5741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/email-client-boomerang-mail/id1236906322</a><br />\n<br />\n即係例如預左今晚會搞到 23:00, 就 send 個 23:30 既 mail send 俾信得過既人<br />\n如果無事, 23:00 就開番個 app, cancel 左個 mail<br />\n萬一唔記得左, 最多都係個 friend 打俾你睇你有無事<br />\n**但 makesure 個 friend 係有習慣 check email 先好"}]}